text: Seth Michael Magaziner ( ; born July 22, 1983) is an American businessman and politician. He has been the U.S. representative for since 2023. He is a member of the Democratic Party. He was the 31st general treasurer of Rhode Island from 2015 until 2023. ==References== ==Other websites== * Congressman Seth Magaziner official U.S. House website * Seth Magaziner for Congress campaign website * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Rhode Island Category:Businesspeople from Rhode Island Category:People from Cranston, Rhode Island Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
